{
  "texts": [
    "Users can provide feedback as they use the system.",
    "Such feedback can then be incorporated into the system after the developer reviews it and prioritizes it.",
    "Furthermore, since such a recommender system is AIbased, it will also learn from user interaction over time (Das et al., 2015; Glikson & Woolley, 2020).",
    "This learning process will occur throughout the product's lifetime, ensuring the recommender system remains part of the social media platform.",
    "Therefore, according to our understanding, most improvement iterations should happen automatically with learning algorithms over time (Jüngling et al., 2020)."
  ]
}